						"key": "jfalcone",
						"displayName": "Joe Falcone",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "I just tested this with the latest continuous build 3.2 SDK and the translucent property doesn't seem to be supported.  A workaround is to set the backgroundImage property.",
